          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5990485-abookwormwithwine?shelf=oldies-but-goodies">oldies-but-goodies</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5990485-abookwormwithwine?shelf=murder-mystery-thriller">murder-mystery-thriller</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5990485-abookwormwithwine?shelf=juvenile-fiction">juvenile-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5990485-abookwormwithwine?shelf=crime">crime</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5990485-abookwormwithwine?shelf=drama">drama</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5990485-abookwormwithwine?shelf=whodunnit">whodunnit</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5990485-abookwormwithwine?shelf=badass-women">badass-women</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5990485-abookwormwithwine?shelf=females-sleuthing">females-sleuthing</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5990485-abookwormwithwine?shelf=library-books">library-books</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5990485-abookwormwithwine?shelf=made-me-chuckle">made-me-chuckle</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1834041561" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10004803832592330017">Ah Nancy Drew, an oldie but a goodie! I remember reading these as a young girl and it was one of the only happy moments from my childhood, when I got lost in books such as this series. Wanted to reread them and see if they were as good as I remembered them to be. I was not disappointed! A little cheesy, but it is a juvenile book after all. Gotta love me some Nancy Drew. 🙌🏽</span>

          </span>
        </div>


